   <title>LAHacks&#58; The most bizarre hackathon experience in my life</title>
   <link href="http://journal.madebychip.com/blog/lahacks-the-most-bizarre-hackathon-experience-in-my-life"/>
   <updated>2014-05-01T00:00:00-07:00</updated>
